Terre_Haute.Deming Woods, Indiana:
Deming Woods is an unincorporated community in eastern Harrison Township, Vigo County, in the U.S. state of Indiana.
Within the boundaries of Terre Haute, it is also part of the Terre Haute metropolitan area.


== Geography ==
Deming Woods is located at 39°27′36″N 87°21′28″W at an elevation of 548 feet.
